name: Int32Array.BYTES_PER_ELEMENT
description: Returns a number value of the element size. 4 in the case of Int32Array.

name: Int32Array.prototype.BYTES_PER_ELEMENT
description: Returns a number value of the element size. 4 in the case of a Int32Array.

name: Int32Array.prototype.constructor
description: The constructor function that created the instance object. For Int32Array instances, the initial value is the Int32Array constructor.
